  "title": "Ore detector",
  "description": "You will be able to know if there are ores underneath.",
  "body": "<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/xNq3q2LY/images/2f0bbce1cf15b95c0ecc98a8d680b989762e7fc8.png\" alt=\"Ore detector banner\"></img>\n\n<h1>What is it about?</h1>\n\nWith this mod, you will be able to obtain various ore detectors, allowing you to know if you have ores underneath.\n\nDepending on the type of detector you have, it can find different types of ores.\n\nIf the detector doesn't find anything, it will make this sound:\n\n<audio controls src=\"https://github.com/restonic4/OreDetector/raw/master/common/src/main/resources/assets/oredetector/sounds/not_found.ogg\" type=\"audio/ogg\" type=\"audio/ogg\"></audio>\n\nIf the detector does find something, it will make this sound:\n\n<audio controls src=\"https://github.com/restonic4/OreDetector/raw/master/common/src/main/resources/assets/oredetector/sounds/found.ogg\" type=\"audio/ogg\"></audio>\n\n<h1>Recipe</h1>\n\nThis is the general crafting recipe; all detectors are crafted this way, but you will need to change the material.\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/xNq3q2LY/images/837f41a434806acfa7a6ccadc951f56b2b57b3da.png\" alt=\"Ore detector recipe\"></img>\n\n<h1>Required mods</h1>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/architectury-api\">Architectury api</a>\nand\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/rest-api\">RestApi</a>\n\n<h1>Videos</h1>\n\n<iframe width=\"315\" height=\"560\"\nsrc=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/H_kMvsWbE24\"\ntitle=\"YouTube video player\"\nframeborder=\"0\"\nallow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\"\nallowfullscreen></iframe>",
